": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036631_1176513656566068_5083145433805685226_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=o3T06zZ9e1UQ7kNvgHmX6QO&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDG7x-ARBbQGgWR4v27OO-kZN71bMDgkpbkUsVJsHoIJQ&oe=66CDD1BF"}, {"file_name": "hamster inc._logo.png", "id": "994291158940421", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75330715_994291162273754_3725985153790783386_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Pe2lPO4VNWYQ7kNvgF1XE9Y&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDV5Etlop95cnqKvRHhY93QqcV2Yy_2LDBAaDICLjxdgA&oe=66CDCA5C"}, {"file_name": "\u6d77\u62a51080x360\u5907\u90097+\u624b.png", "id": "824648603043255", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75195902_824648606376588_6298033056542748118_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7cxCayTGNl4Q7kNvgG6ftl5&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBqp7IvSw8_xFl1dx5LI-GgYidAu96vwatwDkqNkLQ6tg&oe=66CDB68F"}]}, "id": "1382466938967099", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "11.png", "id": "1097797137999292", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570288_1097797141332625_692184632505995617_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=odCVdPGp6J8Q7kNvgGGVHBr&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBuLIad-W2wKgCMqwv2do2Ns4mCSSzOCNHAvy1_pWLz4A&oe=66CDA7F1"}, {"file_name": "2-2560x1440.png", "id": "1631350467404912", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035433_1631350470738245_8852123318308072529_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uoK2Z8lcLRgQ7kNvgE5pnf1&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAb1YKZupfAZbd449fYA9vVGpoS5f3BKbFDuueEZKOHkQ&oe=66CDBD7A"}, {"file_name": "5-2560x1440.png", "id": "471726615347621", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569432_471726618680954_3135093783903181704_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=9uWycEYlVCwQ7kNvgERH4ZQ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAuNUHAnYP8cAsnB9eiZBTRX4x6a1jBBtjInsDLAipUqA&oe=66CDB862"}, {"file_name": "7-2560x1440.png", "id": "1146548799869781", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035337_1146548803203114_4232071023953588234_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=seGiFVTxIsYQ7kNvgGd2EZr&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYApjnok9jRA5TdnnEujXn5cipHIhQRdW64aKLulyPvtow&oe=66CD9EFA"}, {"file_name": "1-2560x1440.png", "id": "999610461677141", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031311_999610465010474_1087177970663193150_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Rp6voYHMTFkQ7kNvgFRwCu8&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBKpsxIVCCXOoCYMCzJSYF-FcpMvVYx647jG3AdqKE4vA&oe=66CDA92B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "2.png", "id": "427799910014327", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75254872_427799913347660_1009234490175775686_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Fvpcl672Vz0Q7kNvgGFJek5&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDCrXwFAtGf5BZUi_cFvziLt33-om6YdV4jmfQSCHOxFQ&oe=66CDA4CF"}, "display_name": "Hamster Inc.", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Welcome to \"Hamster Inc.\"! It's a physics building game that supports \"mixed reality\". In this delightful puzzle game, you'll design, build, and then program machines to overcome challenges!\n\n# Creativity and Logic\n- Based on physical principles and logic, think about how to overcome obstacles and help hamsters improve transportation efficiency.\n{1557136708179895}\n\n# Assembling\n- Design and build a variety of machines with over 60 types of blocks.\n- Over 20 special-function blocks that can be programmed, such as ultrasonic sensors, DC motors, radars and more.\n{327773876776917}\n\n# Graphical programming\n- Super easy! Graphical programming makes your creations \"alive\"!\n{406792278927140}\n\n# Explore 6 unique themes\n- Explore Eastern Forests, Automated factories, Sunshine Coast, Western Gobi, Volcanic Tunnels, and Northern snowfields.\n- As you progress, develop your hamster company and unlock new resources and challenges.\n\n# Enjoy the sandbox mode\n- where you can build and program freely without any limitations on the block amount!\n{971212150879070}\n\n# Mixed Reality\nBring your creations into real world and transform the entire room into a dream paradise: \n- Create custom levels by using real furniture and virtual terrain models, \n- Have your car/drone automatically avoid furniture as it moves around the room,\n- Watch virtual creatures interact with real world: like bison running on tables, floors, or beds!\n{897586709048914}\n\nDiscord: https://discord.gg/NkC8bwQEmK\n", "short_description": "\"Hamster Inc.\" is a physics-based building game that supports \"mixed reality.\"\nIn the game, you can build a variety of interesting inventions such as trebuchets, unmanned trucks, robotic arms, and drones to help the hamsters overcome challenges one after another and continuously develop and expand the logistics territory."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "\u6d77\u62a52560x1440\u5907\u90097-2+logo-\u4e2d\u6587.png", "id": "3772762123041281", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/65229464_3772762126374614_5116127187365598796_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wHuhCFYk240Q7kNvgFSgfvQ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDBHd7S_pXglFwYLApTr14AaYqJHzboH5DL8sFwlyFXgA&oe=66CDA119"}, {"file_name": "icon2.png", "id": "1090290192036087", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57575357_1090290195369420_677972531973123807_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=98rRnBvusY8Q7kNvgEfNTcd&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBcflliTMf1IzchjeNJlf8jPe9F0ux03FhPE4D2GUutCA&oe=66CDC1CD"}, {"file_name": "hamster inc._logo_ch.png", "id": "857711756373822", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/754767